name: Fight for Life
description:
Pencak silat is a traditional martial art originating from the Nusantara Archipelago (Indonesia).
Pencak silat is an amalgamation of elements that represent the personality of the Indonesian nation which is derived from culturalization that has been passed down from generation to generation. Pencak silat is not only about strength and self-defense, but it also builds and develops one's personality and noble character.

I dedicate this work for the 76th Independence Day of Indonesia in 2021.
May it always be a country that liberates its people from misery and injustice.
